                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <h3>Telecommunications</h3>
                                    <div class="border border-danger">
                                        When calling Manila from abroad, phone numbers follow the format: Landline Numbers: +63 2 #### #### Mobile Numbers: +63 9## ### ####
                                        Prepaid mobile SIM cards are widely accessible in airports, malls, and convenience stores. ICPC Manila recommends the services of Smart Communications.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
