                                    <h3>Weather / Climate</h3>
                                    <div class="border border-danger">
                                        The Philippines has a tropical monsoon climate. The month of December falls within the dry season, with occasional rain showers. The average temperature in December falls between 22℃ and 32℃.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <h3>Smoking</h3>
                                    <div class="border border-danger">
                                        Most places in Metro Manila adhere to the Clean Air Act, prohibiting smoking in all open and public spaces. Similarly, enclosed public spaces are smoke-free. The ICPC 2019 venues and Partner Hotels are generally non-smoking. Certain establishments may have a designated smoking area.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <h3>Currency</h3>
                                    <div class="border border-danger">
                                        The Philippine Peso (PHP) is the national currency of the Philippines. Foreign Currency Exchange centers and banks are easily accessible in most parts of the country.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <h3>Registration Inclusions</h3>
                                    <div class="border border-danger">
                                        Register your team on the ICPC Web Site. More details may be found in the instructions for coaches.
                                        Pay the registration fee of your team.
                                        Send a copy of your payment transaction to info.discs@ateneo.edu.
                                        You will receive a confirmation regarding your registration through your ICPC account.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
